{"title":"六亿人民尽成钢","authors":["戈壁舟"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人民尽成钢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一座高山没有烈火？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一个村庄不放光？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一块天空没有烧红？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一段地面不发亮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮得长江银水滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮得黄河翻金浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁战士有万万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东海直到昆仑上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼出两把宝剑来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放射着万道霞光："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把叫做和平剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剑一挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山大河献出粮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把叫做降魔剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剑一挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾澎湖出太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国是座大熔炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人民尽成钢。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}